Product tagline:

EdgeLedger — The Performance Journal for Smart Money Traders

2. Product Vision

EdgeLedger is not a diary.

It is a trading performance intelligence system.

Core value:

Help SMC traders answer questions like:

Which strategy actually works for me?

Which session am I profitable in?

When do I lose money?

What setups give my edge?

The product goal:

Turn trade data into actionable trading insights.

3. Target Market

Primary users:

SMC / ICT traders trading:

Forex

Gold

NASDAQ

US30

Skill level:

Intermediate traders.

Beginner traders rarely journal.

Advanced traders already use tools.

So your sweet spot is:

traders trying to become consistent.

