11. Biggest Risks

Be honest about them.

1. Market competition

Trading journals exist.

Your differentiation must be SMC specialization.

2. Traders quit journaling

Most traders stop after a few weeks.

Retention features are critical.

3. Distribution problem

Good product ≠ users.

Marketing is half the job.

